@startuml
!theme plain
title Epic 21 - US83: Define Abilities (Cost/Type/Target)
class AbilityData {
    + ability_id : str
    + cost_type : CostType
    + cost_amount : int
    + cooldown : int
    + effect_type : EffectType
    + targeting_mode : TargetingMode
}
enum CostType {
    MP
    HP
    ENERGY
}
class AbilityRegistry {
    - _abilities : Dict[str, AbilityData>
    + register(ability_data : AbilityData)
}
note right: Registry Pattern
AbilityRegistry --> AbilityData : stores
@enduml